title: Za'atar bread rolls
ingredients: ['160ml warm whole milk (43 degrees C)', '7g active dried yeast', '1 teaspoon caster sugar', '400g plain flour, divided', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '2 tablespoons butter, melted', '2 eggs', '1/2 teaspoon fine sea salt', 'cooking spray', "8 tablespoons za'atar, divided", '80ml olive oil']
